{"id":302766,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-上海维权人士举行第三期免费法律知识学/","date":"2013-07-08T11:02:37Z","modified":"2013-07-08T11:02:37Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士举行第三期免费法律知识学习讲座（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日 中午<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>时 ～<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>时，上海公民免费学习法律知识，推动依法治国第<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>课成功完成。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">61</span><span>名上海公民参加学习，主讲人是赵迪迪老师（第<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>课法律知识主讲人）的妻子高信翠女士。 高 女士多年来在法律方面受 赵迪迪 老师的指导和自己的不懈努力，她愿把学到的法律知识无私地奉献给大家。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>高信翠</span><span>女士的讲课内容如下<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>《民事诉讼法》： <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第三条，适用因财产关系和人身关系的诉讼。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第四十九条，当事人的权利<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>委托代理人、申请回避、提供证据、提起诉讼、查阅材料、复制材料。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第五十八条二，下列人员可以被委托为代理人，<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>一<span lang=\"EN-US\">)  </span>律师，基层法律服务工作者<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>二<span lang=\"EN-US\">)  </span>当事人的近亲属，或者工作人员<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>三<span lang=\"EN-US\">)  </span>当事人所在社区，单位以及有关社会团体推荐的公民。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第<span lang=\"EN-US\">119</span>条，起诉应符合的条件<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第<span lang=\"EN-US\">123</span>条，应当在日内立案或裁定<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>审期<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>一<span lang=\"EN-US\">)  </span>普通程序案：<span lang=\"EN-US\">149</span>条，六个月内审结，可延长六个月。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>二<span lang=\"EN-US\">)  </span>简易程序：<span lang=\"EN-US\">161</span>条，三个月内审结<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>三<span lang=\"EN-US\">)  </span>上诉案件：<span lang=\"EN-US\">176</span>条，三个月内审结<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>四<span lang=\"EN-US\">)  </span>特别程序：<span lang=\"EN-US\">180</span>条，<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>日内审结<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>五<span lang=\"EN-US\">)  </span>审判监督程序：<span lang=\"EN-US\">205</span>条，六个月内提出<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第<span lang=\"EN-US\">209</span>条，检察建议或者抗诉，检察院应当在三个月内进行审查，作出决定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>《行政诉讼法》：<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 1990<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">年10</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月1</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日起</span></span></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span>注：最高人民法院执行《行政诉讼法》若干问题的解释<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第<span lang=\"EN-US\">97</span>条，可以参照民事诉讼法有关规定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>《行政诉讼法》是实体法，程序上参照《民事诉讼法》<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span>原《民事诉讼法》，“公民代理”须经法院许可，本法<span lang=\"EN-US\">P5</span>，第二十九条第二款，新《民事诉讼法》已取消了法院的这一自由裁量权，<span lang=\"EN-US\">P36</span>页第五十八条。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第五条，法院审理行政案件，对具体行政行为是否合法进行审查<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第七条，当事人在行政诉讼中的法律地位平等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>起诉<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>可以先申请复议，也可以直接起诉。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>先申请复议应在二个月内提出，复议决定后<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>日内起诉。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>直接起诉应在三个月内提出，未告知具体内容的，从知道之日起两年内提出。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>法院收到诉状应在七日内立案或裁定，<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第五十七条，一审起诉到法院，三个月内。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第六十条，二审上诉到判决，二个月之内。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>第八十一条，再审案件，适用一审程序，三个月内。适用二审程序，二个月内。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>欢迎大家参加学习法律知识，推动依法治国。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZdUynl9NXjQ/UdpzvvlaWUI/AAAAAAAAk-Q/zHB_gQC8E9k/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%8A%A8%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC3%E8%AF%BE%E9%9B%86%E4%BD%93%E7%85%A7.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZdUynl9NXjQ/UdpzvvlaWUI/AAAAAAAAk-Q/zHB_gQC8E9k/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%8A%A8%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC3%E8%AF%BE%E9%9B%86%E4%BD%93%E7%85%A7.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-byxvy5Uo_XU/Udpzx-f9r1I/AAAAAAAAk-g/YilIkvSD6gs/s1600/P1020642.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-byxvy5Uo_XU/Udpzx-f9r1I/AAAAAAAAk-g/YilIkvSD6gs/s320/P1020642.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wXQnngdlacE/UdpzxMAdHOI/AAAAAAAAk-Y/ho1TmAWj8x4/s1600/P1020644.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wXQnngdlacE/UdpzxMAdHOI/AAAAAAAAk-Y/ho1TmAWj8x4/s320/P1020644.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Htw1B1m3mJM/Udpzyy3V0nI/AAAAAAAAk-o/hIW_d3GdNW4/s1600/P1020646.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Htw1B1m3mJM/Udpzyy3V0nI/AAAAAAAAk-o/hIW_d3GdNW4/s320/P1020646.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zxz5yp-61MY/Udpz09wzurI/AAAAAAAAk-w/1Ll9BGuYLRs/s1600/P1020647.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zxz5yp-61MY/Udpz09wzurI/AAAAAAAAk-w/1Ll9BGuYLRs/s320/P1020647.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-471CtdP8boE/Udpz6wZ5_8I/AAAAAAAAk_A/-RjXlQ3JXu0/s1600/img060.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-471CtdP8boE/Udpz6wZ5_8I/AAAAAAAAk_A/-RjXlQ3JXu0/s320/img060.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SH4ivR5ZT-c/Udpz42NGAEI/AAAAAAAAk-4/9OSVF63f9EA/s1600/img061.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SH4ivR5ZT-c/Udpz42NGAEI/AAAAAAAAk-4/9OSVF63f9EA/s1600/img061.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}